==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A [[boat]] that has [[sunk]] or run [[aground]] so that it is no longer [[seaworthy]].
#An event where a ship sinks or runs aground.
===Translations===
*Greek: [[ναυάγιο]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#To [[wreck]] a [[boat]] through a [[collision]] or [[mishap]].

